title: Dream Interpretations (Gustavus Hindman Miller) DM
description:
Information:
Author: Gustavus Hindman Miller
Genre/Category: New Age
Usage: Standard Copyright
Ebook Format: PDF

Synopsis:
This is a Dream Dictionary: an A - Z guide containing interpretations of the subjects and situations that may
appear in your dreams. The text is taken from the author's comprehensive work, 10,000 Dreams Interpreted.
Because it was written in America at the turn of the last century we have included this book purely for your
entertainment. Although it represents popular understanding about dreams during that period, the essence
of the interpretations may nevertheless be useful to you.
